results.name: Self-inverse and multiplicative permutation of natural numbers, A235041-conjugate of balanced bit-reverse: a(n) = A235042(A057889(A235041(n))).
comment: a(n) has the same prime signature as n: The permutation maps primes to primes, squares to squares, cubes to cubes, and so on. Permutation A234748 shares the same property.
